{"tid":2412008,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瑞銀警告：比特幣是泡沫     摩根大通：比特幣漲勢不可持續","createTime":"2021-02-17T18:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T22:46:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0f9109162633099ab63f4518d26402245f7cd5","tid":2412008,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T18:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Vv5DQ1f_smdWrtD0IXCkSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMi40NjgwODUxMDYzODM-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/c8150340-70f9-11eb-b5e7-ea6e6acb7633\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVv5DQ1f_smdWrtD0IXCkSA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMi40NjgwODUxMDYzODM-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2Fc8150340-70f9-11eb-b5e7-ea6e6acb7633&h=e0693c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比特幣升破5萬美元，全城雄心壯志要炒bitcoin，有人話5萬好高，有人就話5萬只係10萬嘅一半，平均價入實無死，今日亦有多個群組不約而同彈出教學，叫人開比特幣交易平台。<br />\n<br />\n全城熱炒bitcoin<br />\n雖然，今波升勢與早前大摩傳出其規模1500億美元的投資部門正考慮投資比特幣有關，然而瑞銀最新分析就「企硬」大潑冷水，銀財富管理董事總經理兼多資產策略師Kiran Ganesh的觀點概要如下：<br />\n<br />\n比特幣不如黃金是避險工具（portfolio diversifier）<br />\n<br />\n比特幣太浮動也難避險變現<br />\n<br />\n比特幣不是貨幣，價值難超過零<br />\n<br />\n比特幣太受社網絡影響價格<br />\n<br />\n泡沫的特徵是，投資者只求炒高幣價，而非投資本身有所作用<br />\n<br />\n投資者總有一天會察覺比特幣毫無價值，而投資卻是要有價值<br />\n<br />\n以上原因，對已經「心雄」的投資者來說，就當作是一種參考吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VKJWmjxk9AHYB_aNTURfFg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/ChAo.55R637o0WfvB0mC8A--~B/aD02NzU7dz0xMjAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d1116a88ac39f2873351e485bb43b633\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVKJWmjxk9AHYB_aNTURfFg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FChAo.55R637o0WfvB0mC8A--~B%2FaD02NzU7dz0xMjAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fbloomberg_chinese_traditional_757%2Fd1116a88ac39f2873351e485bb43b633&h=090db4a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【彭博】-- 摩根大通稱，比特幣若要維持漲勢，需降低波動。<br />\n<br />\n摩根大通策略師Nikolaos Panigirtzoglou等人在周二報告中稱，除非波動程度迅速下降，否則當前價格「看起來難以為繼」。<br />\n<br />\n比特幣迭創新高，周三升至51,000美元上方。特斯拉最近宣布投資15億美元，以及MicroStrategy Inc.計畫通過出售6億美元可轉換債券來增持比特幣，加劇了圍繞加密貨幣的狂熱情緒。另一方面，有人認為當前的狂熱可能會像2017年那樣黯淡收場。<br />\n<br />\n摩根大通表示，儘管過去五個月機構資金整體流入規模僅有110億美元左右，但同期比特幣市值成長大約7,000億美元。Panigirtzoglou寫道，比特幣的有限供應和散戶需求可能是當前價格推手。<br />\n<br />\n「1月以來的價格走勢似乎更多是受投機資金流影響，」報告寫道。"},{"pid":"b3f6d86aa8220e2965e0e3ad6399706a4478be89","tid":2412008,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T18:05:21.000Z","msg":"股票呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568f63d394922bba9eb8a1b66dbee31cc65db21f","tid":2412008,"uid":142763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c0f9109162633099ab63f4518d26402245f7cd5","tid":2412008,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T18:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Vv5DQ1f_smdWrtD0IXCkSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMi40NjgwODUxMDYzODM-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/c8150340-70f9-11eb-b5e7-ea6e6acb7633\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVv5DQ1f_smdWrtD0IXCkSA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMi40NjgwODUxMDYzODM-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2Fc8150340-70f9-11eb-b5e7-ea6e6acb7633&h=e0693c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比特幣升破5萬美元，全城雄心壯志要炒bitcoin，有人話5萬好高，有人就話5萬只係10萬嘅一半，平均價入實無死，今日亦有多個群組不約而同彈出教學，叫人開比特幣交易平台。<br />\n<br />\n全城熱炒bitcoin<br />\n雖然，今波升勢與早前大摩傳出其規模1500億美元的投資部門正考慮投資比特幣有關，然而瑞銀最新分析就「企硬」大潑冷水，銀財富管理董事總經理兼多資產策略師Kiran Ganesh的觀點概要如下：<br />\n<br />\n比特幣不如黃金是避險工具（portfolio diversifier）<br />\n<br />\n比特幣太浮動也難避險變現<br />\n<br />\n比特幣不是貨幣，價值難超過零<br />\n<br />\n比特幣太受社網絡影響價格<